craterdog.collections

Class Bag<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • craterdog.collections.abstractions.Collection<E>
      • craterdog.collections.abstractions.OrderedCollection<E>
        • craterdog.collections.Bag<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of element managed by the collection.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Accessible<E>, Iteratable<E>, Ordered<E>, craterdog.core.Composite, craterdog.core.Sequential<E>, Iterable<E>

    public class Bag<E>
extends OrderedCollection<E>
    This collection class implements an ordered collection that allows duplicate elements.
    Author:
    Derk Norton
